First come first served. All items subject to availability or price change. If you've dealt with me then you know there won't be issues...Some items are out at SGC being graded and won't be back for a week or so (the ones I remembered that are there are so marked)...If a card is not graded then I will guarantee it will grade (numerically) by PSA, SGC, or GAI, unless otherwise stated, though I won't guarantee "what" the grade will be..30 days from date of receipt to get it graded, if you so desire.
